<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222650>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Ctenocheloides almeidai sp. nov., holotype, female from Maceió, Alagoas, Brazil (MZUSP 27617): a, dorsal view; b, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222650/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222651>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ctenocheloides almeidai sp. nov., holotype, female from Maceió, Alagoas, Brazil (MZUSP 27617): a, carapace and frontal appendages, dorsal view; b, same, lateral view; c, pleon and tail fan, lateral view; d, telson, dorsal view; e, first maxilliped, lateral view; f, second maxilliped, lateral view; g, detached epipod-like lobe (see text for discussion); h, third maxilliped, lateral view; i, same, ischiomerus, mesial view; j. first pleopod, lateral view; k, second pleopod, lateral view; l, uropod, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222651/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222652>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Ctenocheloides almeidai sp. nov., holotype, female from Maceió, Alagoas, Brazil (MZUSP 27617): a, major (right) cheliped, lateral view; b, same, mesial view; c, same, carpus and chela, dorsal view; d, same, ischium and merus, mesial view; e, major chela fingers closed, lateral view; f, major chela fingers opened, mesial view; g, minor (left) cheliped, lateral view; h, same, mesial view; i, minor chela fingers opened, mesial view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222652/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222653>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Ctenocheloides almeidai sp. nov., holotype, female from Maceió, Alagoas, Brazil (MZUSP 27617): a, second pereiopod, lateral view; b, third pereiopod, lateral view; c, same, propodus and dactylus, mesial view; d, fourth pereiopod, lateral view; e, fifth pereiopod, lateral view; f, same, propodus and dactylus, mesial view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222653/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

